title: Borussia Dortmund’s CEO Hans-Joachim Watzke has dismissed rumours that manager Thomas Tuchel has been approached by Arsenal
text:
EFL Going nowhere Borussia Dortmund’s CEO Hans-Joachim Watzke has dismissed rumours that manager Thomas Tuchel has been approached by Arsenal 
Arsene Wenger's contract with the Gunners runs out at the end of the season and it is believed this could be his final year in charge by jake lambourne
